%%{init: {"theme": "base", "themeVariables": {"fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono", "fontSize": "10px"}, "htmlLabels": false, "flowchart": {"htmlLabels": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant GUI as UCI GUI
    participant Engine as UciEngine run
    participant Pos as Position
    participant TT as TT-Table
    participant Search as search::search

    GUI->>Engine: uci
    Engine-->>GUI: id + options + uciok

    GUI->>Engine: isready
    Engine-->>GUI: readyok

    GUI->>Engine: position startpos moves ...
    Engine->>Pos: new position and apply move list

    GUI->>Engine: setoption name Hash value N
    Engine->>TT: recreate TT with hash size N

    GUI->>Engine: go wtime btime winc binc
    Engine->>Search: search(position, limits, tt, threads)
    Search-->>Engine: SearchInfo(best_move)
    Engine-->>GUI: bestmove uci_move
